$interpreted: Tica: Me~ rry~ Christ~ maaaasssssssss...
Tica: Yikes, it's so~ cold here. Although it is slightly warmer than it used to be, I'm not a winter person. So I'm really bad at dealing with the co~lll~dddd~
Tica: But~ I guess you do need the cold to really bring out that Christmas atmosphere!

Izumi: Nigel, how long do you have to work~
It's not a bad thing to work hard, but sometimes you need to take a break~
Izumi: I know! Let's go out and have a snowball fight!
Yamitsuki: Stop bothering Nigel. If you want to play outside, do it yourself.
Izumi: Aww, don't be mad, Sis Yamitsuki~ We won't leave you behind. Do you want to build a snowman together~
Yamitsuki: ......
Tica: Is anybody home!
Nigel: Who is there?
Tica: Me, me, me, Merry Christmas! Ooh, it's so warm inside here!!
Yamitsuki: Who are you!?
Tica: You don't have to know who I am; you just have to know── that I'm the messenger of love and peace!

Tica: Yeah~ Everybody got their presents!
Then I'll take my leave~ Buh-bye!! Don't miss me too much!!
Yamitsuki: Way too suspicious...
Nigel: Be careful. We don't know where this thing comes from, or what's inside it.
Izumi: Guys, come on~ Don't ruin the mood! You guys think too much. This is just a Christmas present; how dangerous can it be~
Dagger: Where is Tica?!!!!
Dagger: ARGHHHHH! Why always one step behind her!
Dagger: Excuse me, but I'm taking this pile on the floor.
Sherlock: Trying to steal from the great Sherlock's property? In your dreams!

Nigel: Isn't that Sherlock who just ran by?
Can someone tell me what exactly is going on here!?
Izumi: Hoho, this is too interesting. I'm going to follow them to see what the fuss is all about~

Nigel: Tch... I'll go check out the situation as well.
Yamitsuki, you stay here.
Yamitsuki: Nigel!? I'm going too!
